<L>__{interior catacombs}
<A>__{ripley runs, blindly, with panting intensity verging on hysteria. impressions crash upon her...the maze blurring by, sirens howling, the station rocking with explosions, emergency lights flashing, steam blasting, red hot steel hissing. reality itself is reduced to a concussive series of strobelike instants of relentless forward motion. she sees one of the flares she dropped and turns. sees another, sprinting toward it as the foundations of the world shake.}
